snippet.title: BBC Radio 1 INTERVIEWS! FT. Amber Rose Gill, Ovie Soko and Jax Jones
snippet.description:
Hey guys!

I had the pleasure of meeting some amazing people at the BBC Radio 1 Teen Awards and had there opportunity to ask them Reuben's Radio 1 Quick Fire Questions!

💙 Subscribe to my channel: http://bit.ly/ReubendeMaid
💙 Follow me on Instagram: http://bit.ly/ReubenInstagram

👉 Check out my collaboration with SHALOM BLAC: https://youtu.be/TpNOXze6OrU
👉 And my collaboration with AMANDA ENSING: https://youtu.be/3OD2xx4K0ls
👉 More makeup tutorials here: http://bit.ly/MakeupTutorialsPlaylist
👉 Watch me on Ellen meeting Kim Kardashian(!): http://bit.ly/ReubenOnTheEllenShow

💜 My sister is Coco! She loves fashion and sometimes joins me in my videos. She’s awesome, check her out here: http://bit.ly/CocoDeMaid
